Text: RE Gas AgreementinterestingPlease bring me up to speed Im juggling a number of agreements with a number of trading partners Would you mind giving me a little background Normally when we want to trade natural gas Ill work out a GISB Is this a GISB and if so what version Thanks Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday June PM To Subject Gas Agreement Greg Please see the attached draft of the Master Firm PurchaseSale Agreement for your review Upon your review please give me a call to discuss any questions and or comments you may have regarding this matter See attached file Sempra Energydoc Regards Debra Perlingiere Enron North America Corp Legal Department Smith Street EB Houston Texas Phone Fax
